casebody.data:
Youngbird et al., Appellants, v. Whirlpool Corporation, Appellee, et al.

[Cite as Youngbird v. Whirlpool Corp. (1995), 72 Ohio St.3d 1213.]

(No. 94-612 Submitted April 19, 1995 Decided June 7, 1995.) Williams, Jilek, Lafferty & Gallagher Co., L.P.A., and Drew R. Masse, for appellants. Robert M. Anspach Associates, Robert M. Anspach and J. Roy Nunn, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
